WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.226
Good morning, everybody.

00:00:01.226 --> 00:00:09.300
I wanted to come on today and just tell everybody a quick testimony of what God did for us a couple of years ago now.

00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:16.645
We were cleaning the rugs at the church on Saturday, and we were driving home; we were headed home.

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:27.860
The gas gauge on the truck that we had was completely broken, and I didn't realize how low we were on gas.

00:00:28.180 --> 00:00:36.400
We were driving down the highway when, all of a sudden, the truck just went dead and ran out of gas.

00:00:36.660 --> 00:00:41.434
It was probably about 105 degrees in July; it was really hot outside.

00:00:41.434 --> 00:00:49.380
My wife was pregnant with our daughter at the time, and my son and my other daughter were in the back seat.

00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:55.973
As I pulled over, my wife asked, "What's wrong?

00:00:55.973 --> 00:00:59.373
" and I said, "I think we just ran out of gas.

00:00:59.987 --> 00:01:04.327
" We started getting really nervous because it was so hot outside.

00:01:05.122 --> 00:01:16.109
I rolled down the windows and started praying in the Holy Spirit, asking God for mercy because I didn't want to get out of the truck and walk down the highway with a pregnant wife and two kids.

00:01:19.356 --> 00:01:23.664
My son was six and my daughter was 10.

00:01:24.036 --> 00:01:38.340
So I was just praying and, all of a sudden, out of nowhere, I'm holding the steering wheel and I feel this bang on the back of our truck and it jolted us forward.

00:01:38.734 --> 00:01:42.372
I thought we were rear-ended; that's how hard it was.

00:01:42.690 --> 00:01:55.935
I looked in my rearview mirror—and I'm seeing in the spirit at this time—and I see an angel smiling at me in the spirit realm, grinning from ear to ear.

00:01:56.814 --> 00:01:59.560
He was this big, heavy-set guy, kind of like I am; he was chunky-looking.

00:02:08.253 --> 00:02:09.546
He had huge, massive wings spanned out on the back, and he had a hold of my tailgate.

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:19.827
All of a sudden, we started moving supernaturally down the road; he started pushing us faster and faster.

00:02:20.095 --> 00:02:26.006
I was shook up at this time; I was in shock.

00:02:26.006 --> 00:02:32.040
We started moving, and as I held onto the steering wheel, I turned my blinker on to get back on the highway.

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:34.229
My wife's like, "My God, what's going on?

00:02:49.688 --> 00:02:50.022
" We were all just freaking out.

00:03:00.330 --> 00:03:00.760
We were going faster and faster, and I'm in the left-hand lane.

00:03:03.171 --> 00:03:13.410
We were gathering so much speed that we started passing people in the right-hand lane all the way down.

00:03:20.894 --> 00:03:21.292
That angel pushes us three miles to the next gas station.

00:03:22.087 --> 00:03:23.280
We exit the highway.

00:03:26.130 --> 00:03:26.543
We stop at the stoplight.

00:03:26.543 --> 00:03:32.176
He pushes us through the stoplight down the street another block or so.

00:03:35.699 --> 00:03:43.841
We turn right and then we go right into the gas station, and he yanks the tailgate of that truck, and we stop in front of the pump.

00:03:51.284 --> 00:03:51.517
When he did, we all just started screaming and praising God at the pump.

00:03:51.517 --> 00:03:56.259
People at the other pumps were looking at us like, "What is wrong with them?

00:03:56.259 --> 00:04:01.140
" you know, but we were just so excited that we just had an angelic visitation.

00:04:13.034 --> 00:04:13.402
My kids didn't see it, nor did my wife, but we all felt the truck moving.

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:17.999
We were going so fast down the highway; everybody knew it.

00:04:17.999 --> 00:04:23.060
When we got to the pump at the gas station, we all just started worshiping.

00:04:24.192 --> 00:04:25.139
It was just a really cool moment.

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:28.611
Everybody was just like, "Wow," and we all just started laughing.

00:04:28.611 --> 00:04:34.340
We just got so full of joy at what God just did.

00:04:47.924 --> 00:04:48.172
So I just wanted to come on and tell everybody this testimony about what happened for my children and me, that the Lord took care of us.

00:04:48.172 --> 00:04:59.150
We didn't have to have my wife go through it by herself in the middle of the heat and do all that.

00:05:07.840 --> 00:05:08.160
It was a dangerous situation and he came through for us.

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:14.280
So I just wanted to tell everybody about the goodness of God and what He does.

00:05:15.640 --> 00:05:19.193
If you believe, all things are possible to him that believes.

00:05:28.823 --> 00:05:33.127
And nothing's too big for God.

00:05:39.167 --> 00:05:39.393
I have testimony after testimony that I'm going to document.

00:05:39.393 --> 00:05:45.276
I'm going to put them on here so people can hear about the goodness of God and what He's still doing today.

00:05:45.276 --> 00:05:48.568
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:05:48.568 --> 00:05:51.320
And the miracles that He did two thousand years ago, He will still do today if you believe Him for them.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I believe with all my heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
I've seen it time and time again, and I'm going to tell you about each one of them.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Stay tuned.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.450
Thank you for watching, and if you could give us a thumbs up, a like, or a share, it really helps us with the algorithms on YouTube.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
They try to suppress some of my videos and I'm trying to get them out there for the people.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
I really believe God put me on this platform to help folks in these last days.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
There's a lot that I have inside of me to help people, and I want to get it out there.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
So if you could help us if you want to.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
All right, thank you so much for watching.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Have a blessed day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye.
